snippet: In her first round of the season, top-ranked Lydia Ko shot a three-under-par 69 in the Coates Golf Championship in Ocala, Fla., leaving her four strokes behind the leader, Ha Na Jang.
abstract: Ha Na Jang leads Coates Golf Championship in Ocala, Fla.
lead_paragraph: In her first round of the season, top-ranked Lydia Ko shot a three-under-par 69 in the Coates Golf Championship in Ocala, Fla., leaving her four strokes behind the leader, Ha Na Jang.
